282
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,500
[I did it!]

283
00:09:24,850 --> 00:09:25,480
Wait.

284
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:27,700
It's too low.

285
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,100
