286
00:09:30,450 --> 00:09:33,430
C... CEO.

287
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:33,420
[CEO Cha Taehyun] ← [What Boyoung envisions]

288
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:36,540
[Park Boyoung: The "CEO" should be small.]

289
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,960
You know, without any sketches or groundwork,

290
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,970
I'm just pasting them with gusto.

291
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:44,980
[Pasting the words with gusto]

292
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:42,600
It does work.

293
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:44,070
It's not impossible.

294
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,740
[Ah, of course it works! Ha]

295
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:51,140
[CEO]
[With zero hesitation]

296
00:09:47,190 --> 00:09:47,860
No problem.

297
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:55,020
[As expected, there's nothing that is only bad.]

298
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:55,740
[Cha]

299
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,060
[Ah, this is bad.]

300
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:01,700
[It's to wish that his spirits keep rising.]

301
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,890
[What should I do?
There's really no space for "Hyun."]

302
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:09,790
[CEO Cha Tae]
[How high are you going to go?]

303
00:10:09,850 --> 00:10:11,370
Without any sketches or groundwork,

304
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:13,090
[Full of gusto at first]

305
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,260
I'm just pasting them with gusto.

306
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:17,480
[CEO Cha Taehyun]
[Bad at crafts]

307
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:19,300
I'm screwed! Wait.

308
00:10:20,230 --> 00:10:22,310
[I have to decorate it quickly!]

309
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,910
To hide the flaws,

310
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:25,360
[CEO Cha Taehyun]

311
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,330
I have to use my mother-of-pearl stickers.

312
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,150
Quickly.

313
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,020
[Doesn't it look too unimpressive?]

314
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,060
A little...

315
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:33,760
[It makes the CEO look unimpressive.]

316
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,370
Like...

317
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:37,220
[It's not a tiger that goes "Roar!"]

318
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,790
[I'll just paste the tigers randomly.]

319
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:39,720
OK.

320
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,530
Oh, there are such stickers too.

321
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:42,530
[Pastes a pine tree]

322
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:46,370
[I didn't give him orchids,
so I'll paste orchid stickers too]

323
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:49,070
[After pasting more stickers, it looks better.]

324
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:51,360
When unsure, just go for maximalism.

325
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:51,090
[Here you go]

326
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:52,190
Maximalism.

327
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,300
[Here you go]

328
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:57,430
[Pasting stickers casually]

329
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:54,950
CEO.

330
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:56,600
Just...

331
00:10:58,520 --> 00:10:59,280
Done!

332
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,260
I'll leave it far away.

333
00:11:00,180 --> 00:11:04,370
[Boyoung's nameplate with an unpolished charm]

334
00:11:01,610 --> 00:11:03,270
Don't look at it up-close.

335
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:06,990
[Still quite satisfactory]

336
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,820
OK.

337
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:14,820
[Since he's the king of his agency.]

338
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:19,840
[Wraps up the seal carefully]

339
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,630
It's really all done.

340
00:11:20,090 --> 00:11:24,280
[CEO Cha Taehyun] [Completed the gift
[that will bring illuminate (?) his CEO desk]

341
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:24,170
I just need to deliver them now.

342
00:11:25,090 --> 00:11:26,210
-Tae-eun. -Where do I go?

343
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:26,410
[Right ahead.]

344
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:27,250
[Right ahead!]

345
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,040
Right ahead.

346
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,870
[Tae-eun's just leaving cram school after class]

347
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:28,800
I...

348
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,740
Get in quickly.

349
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:33,370
[All smiles at the sight of his helper again]

350
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:34,970
[Sorry.]

351
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:35,790
I'm sorry.

352
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:38,460
[04:07 PM: His helper joins him
straight after cram school classes]

353
00:11:35,990 --> 00:11:37,320
You've to join me again.

354
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:40,810
[What were you going to eat with your friends?]

355
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:40,550
I don't know.

356
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:42,390
But we made a bet to lose weight.

357
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,960
[I can't have spicy hotpot.]
[You can't?]

358
00:11:44,770 --> 00:11:46,800
-We made a bet. -Put on your seat belt first.

359
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:50,980
[Heading to her English cram school first]

360
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,460
Where should I ask Yoohyun to meet us at?

361
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:50,990
The café in front of your English cram school.

362
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:52,890
[Yoohyun, meet me at the cram school.]

363
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:56,180
[Plans to meet another helper
at the café in front of their cram school]

364
00:11:53,170 --> 00:11:55,630
-The cram school. -Our English cram school.

365
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:59,220
-You have to give another gift for me. -Now?

366
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,360
Not now.

367
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:02,150
[Briefs her on her next mission
as soon as she gets in the car]

368
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,070
Just write a card for me.

369
00:12:02,230 --> 00:12:03,320
Like a letter from a teenage fan to her idol.

370
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:07,240
[Second gift:
a teenage fan letter of support for Kang Hoon]

371
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:05,270
A fan letter.

372
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,250
Oh, that card.

373
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,560
[Yoohyun's really good at that.]

374
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,190
[Yoohyun's written several cards
for the rapper Vinxen.]

375
00:12:12,430 --> 00:12:15,370
[I've found the right person!]

376
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:15,710
Dad, seriously.
You have to give Yoohyun pocket money.

377
00:12:15,690 --> 00:12:19,360
[Heading to the café
after settling on the pay (?)]

378
00:12:15,770 --> 00:12:17,980
Of course I will, if we succeed.

379
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,810
[It's that one (?) That's Yoohyun!]

380
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:22,120
-Where? -That one.

381
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,960
-Wait a minute. OK. -That one.

382
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:25,600
[The second helper is waiting for them]

383
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,010
Roll down the car window.

384
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:26,980
[Yoohyun!]

385
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:31,330
[Choi Yoohyun: the second helper,
a.k.a Tae-eun's friend]

386
00:12:31,570 --> 00:12:34,760
[Dad, I feel much more at ease
with Yoohyun here.]

387
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:37,310
Also, call your English cram school now.

388
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:38,820
[Since it's come to this, I'll just skip it.]

389
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:40,250
[No, you can't skip it!]

390
00:12:40,330 --> 00:12:41,910
No, no, no, no, no.

391
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:41,800
[Humph]

392
00:12:42,010 --> 00:12:45,340
You have to deliver these letters
after your classes.

393
00:12:45,700 --> 00:12:47,310
[Then we can't do our homework.]

394
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:50,150
[Screw homework!]

395
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,360
Let's go straight to the gym.

396
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:53,430
Write messages of support to Kang Hoon.

397
00:12:53,690 --> 00:12:55,380
[Am I his fan now?]

398
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,780
-Yeah. -You...

399
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,900
[Whispering]

400
00:12:58,150 --> 00:13:00,460
[But, Dad, what does he do?]

401
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:01,770
-What does he do? -What does he do?

402
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:05,050
[Unexpectedly low fame level...]

403
00:13:02,310 --> 00:13:02,860
Actor.

404
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:04,220
He's an actor.

405
00:13:04,310 --> 00:13:05,110
He's an actor?

406
00:13:05,430 --> 00:13:07,180
Ah, it's because you've never seen this.

407
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:09,620
He was in the drama "A Time Called You."

408
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:10,450
[You don't know how great an actor our Hoon is...]

409
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:11,940
[I watched "Little Women"!]

410
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,920
[I watched "The Red Sleeve" too!]

411
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:15,290
[Oh, I watched that too!]

412
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,590
[Luckily, Uncle Kang Hoon
isn't a total stranger to them]

413
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,290
-Found it. -Found it!

414
00:13:18,810 --> 00:13:21,960
["I'll always support you."
Just keep writing supportive words!]

415
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,370
[Support letter ghostwriters]

416
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:26,900
In the end, I didn't do anything.

417
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:28,950
[Enjoying a cup of coffee leisurely
thanks to his great daughter]

418
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:32,490
[Do you know you wrote "oppa" here and here,
and then "Uncle" here?]

419
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:33,780
-I'll change it to "oppa." -It doesn't matter.

420
00:13:33,780 --> 00:13:35,110
-It doesn't matter. -"Oppa."

421
00:13:35,110 --> 00:13:38,380
[To Uncle Kang Hoon] → [To Kang Hoon-oppa]
[The girls are putting much thought into it]

422
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:37,060
"Oppa."

423
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:40,500
Ah, as expected of Yoohyun who is

424
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:44,650
experienced in fan letters. It's long. -No, no.

425
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:43,760
[Like a pro at giving gifts]

426
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:48,210
[To Kang Hoon-oppa. I'm in middle school
and I'm a fan of yours!]

427
00:13:48,620 --> 00:13:50,620
[Impressed by her writing!]

428
00:13:50,850 --> 00:13:52,520
[Is it OK to lie so blatantly? Haha]

429
00:13:52,090 --> 00:13:52,800
No, you can just become a fan from now on!

430
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,200
[Innocent]

431
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:54,490
It's true that we're fans in middle school!

432
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:56,890
[Cha Taehyun: Just be his fan from now on.]

433
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:56,890
-Exactly. -Right.

434
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:59,620
[Write that you're the vice president (VP)
of the student council too!]

435
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,280
Ah! I'll rewrite it.

436
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:01,690
-Like this. -OK, OK.

437
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:03,950
-Student Council VP. -Student Council VP.

438
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:04,690
[To make a good impression on Uncle Kang Hoon]

439
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:09,570
[I'll write that I'm the confidant
of the Student Council VP.]

440
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:13,290
-That's the letter. And what you said... –S*gle?

441
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:13,870
[Thinking about gifts to give with the letters]

442
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,020
That and...

443
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:16,560
[(Taehyun's daughter) Cha Tae-eun:
Why don't you buy him S*gle?]

444
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:16,620
What's that?

445
00:14:16,770 --> 00:14:17,990
[Fabric deodorizer!]

446
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,530
A gift that doesn't feel like it's from a dad.

447
00:14:19,530 --> 00:14:21,370
-OK. -Something sweet.

448
00:14:21,450 --> 00:14:23,930
If it's from you, besides this,

449
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:25,540
[Strategizes to buy gifts that
seem to have come from young teenagers]

450
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:25,600
what else would be a good gift?

451
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,930
Dad, we're teenagers.

452
00:14:26,850 --> 00:14:30,440
[We usually don't have much money,
so we buy cheap stuff.]

453
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:37,280
[Gifts recommended by teenage girls]

454
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,310
-Lipbalm. -Lipbalm.

455
00:14:32,370 --> 00:14:33,470
That's a common gift.

456
00:14:33,470 --> 00:14:34,800
Lip balm, hand cream...

457
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,710
Prune juice?

458
00:14:36,330 --> 00:14:37,590
Who gives prune juice as a gift?

459
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:40,070
[I want to give him the deepest support]

460
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,470
Something that shows support.

461
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:40,160
Support?

462
00:14:40,310 --> 00:14:42,820
[If we give him the support letters and the gift,
doesn't that show support?]

463
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:44,330
[That's true, but...]

464
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:45,820
[How about flowers?]

465
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:47,750
[We don't have much money,]

466
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,590
[so just one or two stalks?]

467
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,830
[So it's like it's from you kids?]

468
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,560
-Yes... -Listen.

469
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,660
[Put on masks when you go deliver the gifts.]

470
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:55,900
Pretend to be teenage fans.

471
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:59,530
[Concept of gradually increasing number
of teenage fans]

472
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:59,570
Only one person delivered gifts earlier,
but now there are two.

473
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,850
[But what if he chases after us again?]

474
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:04,580
[Remember what I said just now?]

475
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,830
[Pretend you don't know me!]

476
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,060
[Stunned]

477
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:11,470
[Cha Taehyun: He can't know that I'm your dad.]

478
00:15:10,610 --> 00:15:11,670
I can't get caught.

479
00:15:12,230 --> 00:15:14,650
[Dad, will you give us pocket money?]

480
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:14,900
Of course, I'll give it to you now.

481
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:15,830
Asking your dad?

482
00:15:16,310 --> 00:15:19,440
[Yoohyun also gets a share for helping]

483
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:19,630
Share it with Yoohyun,
because she's helping me too.

484
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,470
[Cha Taehyun: I'll wire you 50,000 won first.]

485
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:23,590
I'll give you another 50,000 won if you succeed.

486
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:24,420
[Promises a cash incentive if they meet the goal]

487
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:24,600
Another 50,000 won?

488
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,380
[But you have to succeed.]

489
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,550
[You won't give it if we fail?]

490
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:30,190
No, I will.

491
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:33,100
-I think he'll fall for this. -I love you.

492
00:15:33,850 --> 00:15:34,520
OK.

493
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:37,230
[Before they know it, it's time for cram school]

494
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:35,760
Done.

495
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:36,840
I'm a teenage fan.

496
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:38,210
Hurry up and go.

497
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:42,580
It's 4:30 PM now.
Later at 6 PM, let's meet here again.

498
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:42,830
[Sets a time to meet again after their class]

499
00:15:43,110 --> 00:15:45,070
-Yay! Yay! -Here?

500
00:15:45,130 --> 00:15:45,710
Got it?

501
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,000
-Bye, Dad! -Goodbye.

502
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,600
Bye. Thank you for your help.

503
00:15:49,010 --> 00:15:50,240
[I have to make a move quickly!]

504
00:15:50,490 --> 00:15:51,790
[Hwang Kwanghee: Is "Pea" her nickname?]

505
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,360
[To Pea] [Pea's birthday] [(Pea emoticon)]

506
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:55,710
Oh, Sunbin, so Sun-bean!

507
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,710
[T/N: "Pea" in korean includes
the character for "bean"]

508
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:58,730
